data.title: Alaska Press Club
data.meta_description: Alaska Press Club Awards Announcing the recipients of the 2024 Alaska Press Club Awards. CONGRATULATIONS! Awards Winners PDF (Please do not contact the judges.) Award Winners PDF with judges comments. 2024 Contest Guide We've received some great feedback from our judges on the quality of entries in the Alaska Press Club Awards for 2021. Here's…
data.text:
“Judging this contest felt like a near-impossible task. Almost all of the entries could have earned first-place recognition. It’s comforting to know the residents of Alaska have such capable watchdogs holding the criminal justice system accountable.”

Judge for Best Legal Affairs Reporting

“Having judged countless competitions, I am not exaggerating in saying that viewers of television news in Alaska are the beneficiaries of some of the finest feature reporting anywhere.”

Judge for TV Best Feature

“I’ve been a contest judge for more than 15 years and in multiple states. This is the most compelling, robust environmental reporting I have ever seen. The competition this year went above and beyond anything I had hoped to watch, listen to or read as a judge. I must salute all of the journalists who submitted entries in this category. Your work goes beyond Alaska to issues about which all Americans should be informed. Really well done!”

Judge for Best Environmental Reporting
